name: CUBE FALL (michelescara)
description:
CUBE FALL is a nice and addictive platformer, with just one easy goal: let the cube enter in the hole. There are many different levels to play, and there is also a shop system to repay your efforts! What are you waiting for? Download it!

P.S.

The game is still in development, so please help me with some donations to make the development go on!
